<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$caizhongyuan" href="/people/caizhongyuan">蔡中元</a>，<strong title="心理教育工作者" class="zu-question-my-bio">心理教育工作者</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="4">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-jia-wei-23-75" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-jia-wei-23-75" class="zg-link" title="张佳伟">张佳伟</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$qian-xiang-chen" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/qian-xiang-chen" class="zg-link" title="钱相臣">钱相臣</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$Kevin071" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/Kevin071" class="zg-link" title="刘晓">刘晓</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="596904" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">妻不如妾，妾不如偷，偷不如不偷，就是这个道理，<strong>幻想总能比现实更美好。</strong><br><br>人常犯的错就是有美好的期待，却没有最坏的打算。<br><br>调整期望值是不错的做法，Hope for the best，and plan for worst。 <br><br>悲观主义的叔本华认为，人就是在痛苦和无聊之间摇摆，欲望不满足就痛苦，欲望一满足就无聊。也许不是你得到的东西变得和你期待的不一样，只是你得到之后你渐渐觉得无聊了，是你对得到的东西感受发生变化，而不是它不一样了。
<a href="/question/21040939/answer/16978904" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

